FIG. 1 provides a pictorial representation of a user driving an ATV embodying the present invention;


FIG. 2 is a diagrammatic side elevation view of the ATV seen in FIG. 1, with the vehicle shown partially in phantom lines to allow the layout of the engine and power train of the vehicle to be seen;


FIG. 3 is a plan view of the ATV seen in FIGS. 1 and 2, and is also shown partially in phantom lines to better illustrate the engine and power train layout of the vehicle; and


FIG. 4 provides a fragmentary cross sectional elevation view of a transmission gear unit of the ATV seen in the preceding drawing Figures.
